== 演化 ==
美洲豹是豹属动物在[[新大陸|新大陆]]上现存的唯一成员。[[脱氧核糖核酸|脱氧核糖核酸（DNA）]]分析结果表明：狮、虎、[[豹|花豹]]、美洲豹、雪豹还有云豹拥有共同的祖先，这一科动物的发展历经600到1000万年<ref name=Johnson2006>{{cite journal |author=Johnson, W. E. |author2=Eizirik, E. |author3=Pecon-Slattery, J. |author4=Murphy, W. J. |author5=Antunes, A. |author6=Teeling, E. |author7=O'Brien, S. J. |year=2006 |doi=10.1126/science.1122277 |title=The Late Miocene radiation of modern Felidae: A genetic assessment |journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |volume=311 |pages=73–77 |pmid=16400146 |issue=5757 |bibcode=2006Sci...311...73J |url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/473f6d3685451ace84ebc51ac3ab21ab9923f54d |access-date=2020-01-13 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124130302/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/The-Late-Miocene-Radiation-of-Modern-Felidae:-A-Johnson-Eizirik/473f6d3685451ace84ebc51ac3ab21ab9923f54d |dead-url=no }}</ref>；化石记录却指出，豹属动物的出现只是200万到380万年前的事<ref name=Eizirik>{{cite journal |author=Eizirik, E. |author2=Kim, J. H. |author3=Menotti-Raymond, M. |author4=Crawshaw P. G. Jr. |author5=O'Brien, S. J. |author6=Johnson, W. E. |year=2001 |title=Phylogeography, population history and conservation genetics of jaguars (''Panthera onca'', Mammalia, Felidae) |journal=Molecular Ecology |volume=10 |issue=1 |doi=10.1046/j.1365-294X.2001.01144.x |pmid=11251788 |pages=65–79 |url=https://semanticscholar.org/paper/5bd14c9ccc8cc43ed15352fc86075b8d6b8cccee |access-date=2020-01-13 |archive-date=2021-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129021257/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Phylogeography%2C-population-history-and-conservation-Eizirik-Kim/5bd14c9ccc8cc43ed15352fc86075b8d6b8cccee |dead-url=no }}</ref>。人们认为豹属动物是在[[亚洲|亚洲]]演化形成的。美洲豹则被认为是在距今至少150万年以前，从豹属动物的共同祖先里分化出来，它们在[[更新世|更新世]]早期，通过曾横亘[[白令海峡|白令海峡]]的[[白令陸橋|白令陆桥]]，进入美洲大陆。对美洲豹的[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]做分析发现，这一物种的进化发生在28万到51万年前。

[[系统发生学|系统发育]]研究已广泛证明，云豹（拉丁名：Neofelis nebulosa）是这个族群中的[[基群|基群]]<ref name=Janczewski>{{cite journal |author1=Janczewski, D. N. |author2=Modi, W. S. |author3=Stephens, J. C. |author4=O'Brien, S. J. |year=1996 |title=Molecular evolution of mitochondrial 12S RNA and cytochrome b sequences in the pantherine lineage of Felidae |journal=[[Molecular_Biology_and_Evolution|Molecular Biology and Evolution]] |volume=12 |issue=4 |url=http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/12/4/690 |pmid=7544865 |pages=690–707 |doi=10.1093/oxfordjournals.molbev.a040232 |access-date=2009-07-07 |archive-date=2010-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100501070049/http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/12/4/690 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Johnson1997>{{cite journal |author1=Johnson, W. E. |author2=O'Brien, S. J. |year=1997 |title=Phylogenetic reconstruction of the Felidae using 16S rRNA and NADH-5 mitochondrial genes |journal=Journal of Molecular Evolution |volume=44 |issue=S1 |doi=10.1007/PL00000060 |pmid=9071018 |pages=S98–116 |bibcode=1997JMolE..44S..98J |url=https://zenodo.org/record/1232587 |access-date=2020-01-13 |archive-date=2020-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419112145/https://zenodo.org/record/1232587 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Yu>{{cite journal |author=Yu, L. |author2=Zhang, Y. P. |year=2005 |title=Phylogenetic studies of pantherine cats (Felidae) based on multiple genes, with novel application of nuclear beta-fibrinogen intron 7 to carnivores |journal=[[Molecular_Phylogenetics_and_Evolution|Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution]] |volume=35 |issue=2 |pages=483–495 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2005.01.017 | pmid = 15804417}}</ref>。围绕其余分支地位展开的研究，尚未得出统一结果，也未得到有效确认。

英国动物学家[[雷金納德·英尼斯·波科克|雷金纳德·英尼斯·波科克]]根据形态学上的证据，得出结论——美洲豹和花豹的关系最密切<ref name=Pocock1939/>。然而，人们根据DNA方面的证据，并未得出最终结论；不同研究中，美洲豹和其他物种的关系也存在差异<ref name=Johnson2006/><ref name=Janczewski/><ref name=Johnson1997/><ref name=Yu/>。从灭绝了的豹属物种的化石，如[[歐美洲豹|欧美洲豹]]（拉丁名为Panthera gombaszoegensis）和[[美洲擬獅|美洲拟狮]]（拉丁名为Panthera atrox）的化石可以看出，它们兼具了狮和美洲豹的特点<ref name=Janczewski/>。

== 分类 ==
1758年，[[卡爾·林奈|卡爾·林奈]]在他的著作《[[自然系統|自然系統]]》描述了美洲豹並將其學名以[[二名法|二名法]]命名為''Felis onca''<ref>{{cite book |author=Linnaeus, C. |year=1758 |title=Caroli Linnæi Systema naturæ per regna tria naturæ, secundum classes, ordines, genera, species, cum characteribus, differentiis, synonymis, locis |volume=Tomus I |edition=decima, reformata |location=Holmiae |publisher=Laurentius Salvius |page=42 |chapter=''Felis onca'' |chapterurl=https://archive.org/stream/mobot31753000798865#page/41/mode/2up}}</ref>。

19世纪和20世纪，多个美洲豹模式标本让人们有了描述该生物[[亞種|亚种]]的依据<ref name=MSW3>{{cite book| last = Wozencraft | first = W.C.| year = 2005| chapter = {{{heading|Order Carnivora}}}| chapter-url= http://www.departments.bucknell.edu/biology/resources/msw3/browse.asp?id=14000240| editor1-last=Wilson |editor1-first=D.E. |editor1-link=Don E. Wilson| editor2-last=Reeder |editor2-first=D.M| title = Mammal Species of the World: A Taxonomic and Geographic Reference| url = http://www.google.com/books?id=JgAMbNSt8ikC&pg=PA546–547| pages = 546–547| edition = 3rd | publisher = Johns Hopkins University Press| isbn= 978-0-8018-8221-0| oclc= 62265494| ref = {{{ref|harv}}}}}</ref>。1939年，[[雷金納德·英尼斯·波科克|雷金纳德·英尼斯·波科克]]通过追寻这些标本的地理起源、观察颅骨形态，识别出8个亚种<ref name=Pocock1939>{{cite journal |last1=Pocock |first1=R. I. |year=1939 |title=The races of jaguar (''Panthera onca''). |journal=Novitates Zoologicae |volume=41 |pages=406–422 |url=https://archive.org/details/cbarchive_123320_theracesofjaguarpantheraonca9999}}</ref>。波科克缺乏充足的动物标本，无法很好地评估这些亚种的状态，却表示自己对几个亚种的状态存有疑虑。人们之后对他的工作再作思考后认为，识别出的亚种只有三个。对“P. o. palustris”的描述是基于一块化石颅骨作出的<ref name=Seymour>{{cite journal  |last1=Seymour |first1=K. L. |year=1989 |title=''Panthera onca'' |journal=Mammalian Species |volume=340 |pages=1–9 |doi=10.2307/3504096 |url=http://www.science.smith.edu/departments/Biology/VHAYSSEN/msi/pdf/i0076-3519-340-01-0001.pdf |accessdate=27 December 2009 |issue=340 |jstor=3504096 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620231016/http://www.science.smith.edu/departments/Biology/VHAYSSEN/msi/pdf/i0076-3519-340-01-0001.pdf |archivedate=20 June 2010  }}</ref>。《世界哺乳动物物种》作者，在列出9个亚种和P. o. palustris或称P. o. paraguensis时，把两者区隔开来<ref name=MSW3/>。

[[形態學_(生物學)|形态学]]或[[基因學|基因学]]研究结果表明，美洲豹南北种群存在渐变群差异，但没有证据显示亚种间有差别<ref name=Eizirik/><ref name=Larson>{{cite journal |last1=Larson |first1=S. E. |year=1997 |title=Taxonomic re-evaluation of the jaguar |journal=[[Zoo_Biology|Zoo Biology]] |volume=16 |issue=2 |pages=107–120 |doi=10.1002/(SICI)1098-2361(1997)16:2<107::AID-ZOO2>3.0.CO;2-E}}</ref>。随后更细致的研究，对先前预期的[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]美洲豹种群的结构作出确认<ref name = Columbia/>。

《自然保护联盟濒危物种红色名录》的物种评估员，以及猫科动物专家组负责猫科动物分类任务的团队，认为所有美洲豹亚种均不作数<ref name=iucn/><ref name=catsg>{{cite journal |author1=Kitchener, A. C. |author2=Breitenmoser-Würsten, C. |author3=Eizirik, E. |author4=Gentry, A. |author5=Werdelin, L. |author6=Wilting, A. |author7=Yamaguchi, N. |author8=Abramov, A. V. |author9=Christiansen, P. |author10=Driscoll, C. |author11=Duckworth, J. W. |author12=Johnson, W. |author13=Luo, S.-J. |author14=Meijaard, E. |author15=O'Donoghue, P. |author16=Sanderson, J. |author17=Seymour, K. |author18=Bruford, M. |author19=Groves, C. |author20=Hoffmann, M. |author21=Nowell, K. |author22=Timmons, Z. |author23=Tobe, S. |year=2017 |title=A revised taxonomy of the Felidae: The final report of the Cat Classification Task Force of the IUCN Cat Specialist Group |journal=Cat News |volume=Special Issue 11 |pages=70–71 |url=https://repository.si.edu/bitstream/handle/10088/32616/A_revised_Felidae_Taxonomy_CatNews.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y |access-date=2020-01-13 |archive-date=2018-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730142355/https://repository.si.edu/bitstream/handle/10088/32616/A_revised_Felidae_Taxonomy_CatNews.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

